<li>Hamer, D. A, <i>Liberal politics in the age of Gladstone and Rosebery: a study in leadership and policy</i> (1972).</li>
<li>Langer, William L. <i>The Diplomacy of Imperialism: 1890–1902</i> (2nd ed. 1950), a standard diplomatic history of Europe</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Jenkins,_Roy" class="mw-redirect" title="Jenkins, Roy">Jenkins, Roy</a>. <i>Gladstone: A Biography</i> (2002)</li>
<li>Knaplund, Paul. <i>Gladstone and Britain's Imperial Policy</i> (1966) <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/gladstonebritain0000knap">online</a></li>
